sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student
    participant ESB as ESB Gateway
    participant Academic as Academic Service
    participant Finance as Finance Service
    participant Library as Library Service

    Student->>ESB: GET /api/v1/student/dashboard
    activate ESB
    
    Note over ESB: Fan-out requests (Parallel)
    
    par Fetch Enrollments
        ESB->>Academic: GET /academic/enrollments
        Academic-->>ESB: [Enrollment List]
    and Fetch Invoices
        ESB->>Finance: GET /finance/invoices?status=unpaid
        Finance-->>ESB: [Unpaid Invoice List]
    and Fetch Loans
        ESB->>Library: GET /library/loans
        Library-->>ESB: [Active Loan List]
    end
    
    Note over ESB: Aggregate Data (Max 800ms timeout)
    ESB->>ESB: Combine JSON responses
    
    ESB-->>Student: 200 OK (Aggregated Dashboard Data)
    deactivate ESB
